    "chemicalDescription": [
      "r-(sh/s-Mouse Polypeptide-1 sh-Polypeptide-95)/r-(sh/s-Mouse Polypeptide-2 sh-Polypeptide-118) is the combination of two recombinant fusion peptides, r-(sh/s-Mouse Polypeptide-1 sh-Polypeptide-95) and r-(sh/s-Mouse Polypeptide-2 sh-Polypeptide-118), that make up a type of synthetic non-germline humanized immunoglobulin (antibody) that binds to vimentin. The two chains may have inter-chain and/or intra-chain disulfide bonds."
